## Phase 7: Polish, Responsive & Launch

**Goal:** Final polish, mobile responsiveness, accessibility, performance optimization, and testing.

### UI Polish
- Micro-animations on all interactions (card selections, panel transitions, progress updates)
- Smooth page transitions between sections
- Loading skeletons
- Empty states with helpful guidance
- Error boundaries

### Responsive Design
- Desktop: full 3-panel layout
- Tablet: collapsible left nav, hidden right panel (toggle)
- Mobile: single panel with bottom navigation, swipe between sections

### Accessibility
- Keyboard navigation through all sections
- ARIA labels on all interactive elements
- Focus management
- Screen reader support
- High contrast mode support

### Performance
- Lazy load sections and heavy components
- Memoize expensive computations (search, validation, recommendations)
- Optimize re-renders in option grids
- Bundle size analysis

### Testing & Verification
- Component smoke tests
- Question engine logic tests
- Validation engine tests
- Generation engine tests
- End-to-end flow: create → configure → validate → generate → export
- Cross-browser testing

### Deliverables
- Fully responsive on desktop, tablet, mobile
- Keyboard accessible
- Smooth animations throughout
- All engines tested
- Production-ready build

